### Group - Create (legacy route)
POST {{host}}/group/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Casa 2026",
  "description": "Grupo principal 2026"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("group_id", response.body.id);
%}

###

### Group - Get by id
GET {{host}}/group/{{group_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Group - List my groups (legacy route)
GET {{host}}/group/my-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Group - Members
GET {{host}}/group/{{group_id}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Group - Update group (admin only)
PUT {{host}}/group/{{group_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Casa 2026 Editada",
  "description": "Grupo principal actualizado"
}

###

### Group - Make admin (admin only)
POST {{host}}/group/{{group_id}}/make_admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "new_user_id": "{{other_user_id}}"
}

###

### Group - Delete group (logical delete, admin only)
DELETE {{host}}/group/{{group_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Group - Leave group
POST {{host}}/group/{{group_id}}/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Group - Verify left (should not include the group)
GET {{host}}/group/my-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
